{"id": "1456783552736661564", "channel_id": "1456783552736661564", "type": 0, "author_id": "266297152911835147", "author_name": "null.pointer_exception", "author_bot": false, "content": "I think it would benefit the community for us to be able to use lower enlightment levels to the ones we currently posses. This would make:\n\n- Better guides: since each E can potentially change how a character is played, this would encourage experimentation.\n- More (meaningful) interaction in game-question and team-building: by being able to replicate newbie config to better understand and help them.\n- Fun community challenges: such as lowest investment clear in D-tide.", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T22:57:44.702000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1456783552971804794", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 8973, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1456783552736661564/1456783552971804794/image.png?ex=69ff1328&is=69fdc1a8&hm=c6cf916528a5429c26733eb832818ff96a28c58d3703cbbff5463b8269b2bb03&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456783552736661564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Enlightment Adjustment", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
